In Montgomery County, every ZIP code has a different economic story. The  2022 American Community Survey shows income data like a map that points out where wealth and need are different across Montgomery county. As you look through the data, you see ZIP codes where the median household incomes range from low to high, showing a wide economic range. This shows how different neighborhoods live, with their own economic struggles and financial wins. By seeing where the lower incomes are we can better understand how money status might affect the safety of the area, especially in busy school zones where we need to protect or child.
